- Performance rank is determined by ranking students within their major based on their lowest grade, with the highest grade (A) ranked first and the lowest grade (F) ranked last; 
- The demographic category refers to the student's racial or ethnic group; 
- The role of the manager refers to the role the manager has in the educational institution.

sql:
SELECT demographic_name, demographic_description
FROM demographic_categories
WHERE demographic_id = 1;
